				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Today in Small Business: A Start-Up About Nothing</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Gene Marks			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-08-18T16:46:57+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">August 18, 2014 12:46 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">August 18, 2014 12:46 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/08/18/today-in-small-business-a-start-up-about-nothing/" data-title="Today in Small Business: A Start-Up About Nothing" data-description="A proposed law in California would make it harder for parent companies to sever ties with franchisees. How high-end juices extract high prices from customers. And the creator of the original pop-up ad apologizes.">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>The Economy</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Robert J. Shiller says the stock market <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/08/17/upshot/the-mystery-of-lofty-elevations.html?&amp;abt=0002&amp;abg=1">looks expensive</a> right now and a key ratio is âhovering at a worrisome level.â</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Entrepreneurship</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A beer-induced, miniature golf business idea goes from <a href="//www.mlive.com/business/ann-arbor/index.ssf/2014/08/beer-induced_business_idea_goe.html">concept to reality</a> for two college students.</li>
<li>An entrepreneur explains <a href="//www.theage.com.au/small-business/entrepreneur/this-woman-started-a-retreat-empire-20140722-3cd21.html">how she started</a> her empire of retreats.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Start-Up</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A <a href="//www.forbes.com/sites/ilyapozin/2014/08/14/this-entrepreneur-raised-2m-with-a-five-slide-presentation-about-nothing/">start-up about nothing</a> raises $2 million.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span id="more-87895"></span></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Management</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Here is how a business owner <a href="https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/business-owner-rises-top-pinball-community">rose to the top</a> of the pinball community.</li>
<li>This is why college <a href="//www.businessinsider.com/why-college-textbooks-cost-so-much-2014-8?">textbooks cost so</a> much.</li>
<li>Here are 10 <a href="//www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/08/17/companies-control-food_n_5684782.html">companies that control</a> the world&#8217;s food.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>The Law</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A proposed law in California would make it harder for parent companies to <a href="//www.marketplace.org/topics/economy/owners-franchises-may-get-more-control#.U_IDSlmRq14.twitter">sever ties with franchisees</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Employees</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Female business <a href="//www.usatoday.com/story/travel/roadwarriors/2014/08/17/life-has-changed-for-the-better-for-women-on-the-road/13916755/">travelers are finding a more</a> accommodating world.</li>
<li>A report estimates that <a href="//www.upi.com/Odd_News/2014/08/15/Report-Fantasy-football-season-costs-employers-billions-of-dollars/6071408118188/?spt=su">fantasy football</a> causes more than $13 billion in lost productivity.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Pricing</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Here&#8217;s how high-end juices <a href="//nyti.ms/1sH7TL2">extract high prices</a> from customers.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Social Media</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Twitterâs <a href="//thenextweb.com/twitter/2014/08/17/twitters-latest-experiment-turns-favorites-into-retweets-and-its-annoying-lots-of-people/">latest experiment turns</a> favorites into retweets &#8212; and itâs annoying people.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>The <a href="//venturebeat.com/2014/08/17/the-unbearable-lightness-of-snapchat/">transient nature</a> of Snapchat makes it extremely difficult for marketers to achieve meaningful engagement with users.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Online</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The creator of the <a href="//qz.com/249844/i-created-the-original-pop-up-ad-and-im-sorry/">original pop-up</a> ad apologizes.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Mobile</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Here are three trends <a href="//techcrunch.com/2014/08/16/three-trends-that-will-make-a-difference-in-mobile-payment/">that will make</a> a difference in mobile payments.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Health Care</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>An amazing <a href="//www.businessinsider.com/maryland-health-care-revolution-2014-8">health care revolution</a> is happening in Maryland, and almost no one is talking about it.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Ideas</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>These entrepreneurs <a href="//www.entrepreneur.com/article/236519">found a way</a> to make energy-efficient vodka.</li>
<li>Ralph Lauren introduces a <a href="//www.businessweek.com/articles/2014-08-14/ralph-laurens-all-denim-suit-for-business-dudes?">denim suit</a> for business people.</li>
<li>A sneaky mom <a href="//www.neatorama.com/2014/08/17/Sneaky-Mom-Creates-App-That-Prevents-Her-Teens-from-Using-Their-Phones-Until-They-Call-Her/#!bFdkvx">creates an app</a> that prevents her teens from using their phones until they call her.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Opportunities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Accounting businesses are at <a href="//www.forbes.com/sites/sageworks/2014/08/17/accounting-tops-most-profitbusinesses-top-list-of-money-making-industries/">the top of the list</a> of money-making businesses.</li>
<li>In todayâs sharing economy <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/08/17/technology/in-the-sharing-economy-workers-find-both-freedom-and-uncertainty.html?_r=0">workers are finding</a> both freedom and uncertainty (but a new Federal Aviation Administration ruling <a href="//www.theverge.com/2014/8/16/6009055/new-faa-ruling-effectively-bans-ridesharing-for-planes">effectively bans</a> ride-sharing for planes).</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the Country</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The unrest in Ferguson is <a href="//www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2014/08/16/ferguson-unrest-takes-toll-on-small-business/14167945/">taking its toll</a> on small businesses.</li>
<li>The San Francisco Department of Health is <a href="//www.thestreet.com/story/12846315/1/pot-on-wheels-service-forges-ahead-under-citys-scrutiny.html">reportedly investigating</a> an Uber-like marijuana-delivery app.</li>
<li>Here are 10 places that <a href="//www.marketwatch.com/story/10-places-boomers-and-millennials-are-escaping-from-fastest-2014-08-15">boomers and millennials</a> want to leave.</li>
<li>Researchers are in the process of <a href="//www.houmatoday.com/article/20140815/articles/140819808?">conducting surveys</a> of landowners in Louisiana in an effort to put a dollar figure on the damage being done by feral hogs.</li>
<li>According to a survey, a small chain of barbershops is the best small <a href="//www.delawareonline.com/story/money/business/2014/08/16/us-male-barbershops-top-small-business-work-de/14134229/">employer to work for</a> in Delaware.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the World</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Matt OâBrien <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2014/08/14/europes-greater-depression-is-worse-than-the-1930s/">argues that</a> Europeâs current âdepressionâ is worse than that of the 1930s.</li>
<li>These are the top five <a href="//www.blogto.com/city/2014/08/the_top_5_toronto_inventions_of_all_time/">inventions</a> to come from Toronto.</li>
</ul>
